&lt;li&gt;Experience leading distributed teams across multiple time zones (e.g., US plus Europe or LATAM)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has directly owned performance management cycles, including coaching, leveling, and exiting underperformers&lt;/li&gt;
