&lt;li&gt;Agile/kanban project management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to understand, communicate and improve the quality of multiple teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Humble, servant leader&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
